  <section role="problem">
    <title>Problem</title>
    <para>You need a glossary and want to know all the features.</para>
  </section>
  <section role="solution">
    <title>Solution</title>
    <para>A glossary can be written with the following two elements:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>with <tag
          xlink:href="http://www.docbook.org/tdg51/en/html/glossary.html">glossary</tag>,
          using it as a division element
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>with <tag
          xlink:href="http://www.docbook.org/tdg51/en/html/glosslist.html">glosslist</tag>,
        using it as a block element</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

  </section>
